<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0011: “A” Camshaft Position Timing Over Advanced or System Performance
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measured intake CMP does not reach target intake CMP for specified time.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
OCV and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CKP sensor and sensor plate
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CMP sensor
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
OCV oil passage
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CMP actuator
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Valve timing
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0014: “B” Camshaft Position Timing Over Advanced or System Performance
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measured exhaust CMP does not reach target exhaust CMP for specified time.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
